message.body: I snagged one of those pens from work that Gillian liked. I'll drop it off sometime.
Awesome. You didn't have to do that. We are here all weekend except Gillian is gone Sunday. What are you guys up to this weekend?
Nothing planned. You and Gillian feel like coming by tomorrow?
Oh I forgot, making pizza and watching football was also scheduled today. How'd the table come out?
Great. I got a bar tending Job tonight so I'm working
Very cool, if it was a bar somewhere local I would have stopped by on my run.
